#. module: account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account.field_account_journal__type
msgid ""
"\n"
"        Select 'Sale' for customer invoices journals.\n"
"        Select 'Purchase' for vendor bills journals.\n"
"        Select 'Cash', 'Bank' or 'Credit Card' for journals that are used in "
"customer or vendor payments.\n"
"        Select 'General' for miscellaneous operations journals.\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"        Välj \"Försäljning\" för journaler som hanterar kundfakturor.\n"
"        Välj \"Inköp\" för journaler som hanterar leverantörsfakturor.\n"
"        Välj 'Kontanter', 'Bank' eller 'Kreditkort' för journaler som "
"används vid kund- eller leverantörsbetalningar.\n"
"        Välj \"Allmänt\" för journaler som hanterar diverse verksamhet.\n"
"        "

#. module: account
#: model:ir.model.fields,help:account.field_account_tax__amount_type
msgid ""
"\n"
"    - Group of Taxes: The tax is a set of sub taxes.\n"
"    - Fixed: The tax amount stays the same whatever the price.\n"
"    - Percentage: The tax amount is a % of the price:\n"
"        e.g 100 * (1 + 10%) = 110 (not price included)\n"
"        e.g 110 / (1 + 10%) = 100 (price included)\n"
"    - Percentage Tax Included: The tax amount is a division of the price:\n"
"        e.g 180 / (1 - 10%) = 200 (not price included)\n"
"        e.g 200 * (1 - 10%) = 180 (price included)\n"
"        "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    - Skattegrupp: Skatten är en samling av skatter.\n"
"     - Fast summa: Skattebeloppet är detsamma oavsett grundbeloppet.\n"
"     - Procentuell skatt: Skattebeloppet är en procentandel av "
"grundbeloppet:\n"
"        t.ex. 100 * (1 + 10%) = 110 (pris exklusive skatt)\n"
"        t.ex. 110 / (1 + 10%) = 100 (pris inklusive skatt)\n"
"     - Procentuell skatt inkluderad: Skattebeloppet är en andel av priset:\n"
"        t.ex. 180 / (1 - 10%) = 200 (pris exklusive skatt)\n"
"        t.ex. 200 * (1 - 10%) = 180 (pris inklusive skatt)\n"
"        "

